Package org.moeaframework.core.termination

Defines conditions for terminating runs.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
CompoundTerminationCondition Terminates a run when one or more termination conditions are satisfied.
MaxElapsedTime Terminates a run when the maximum elapsed time is exceeded.
MaxFunctionEvaluations Terminates a run when the maximum number of function evaluations is exceeded.
